      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i cant really get to a doctor right now because of work. i just want to know if the timing makes sense. i read online that keeping a steady level in your system is better than waiting for the pain to hit, so taking it every 2 hours seems logical for the 400mg dose. is there any reason why i shouldn't just do that to manage the inflammation?",
